nodes.prompt:
Given this review task:
{{task}}

Identify 2-6 concrete targets to inspect (modules, packages, or areas). Return structured JSON with a "targets" array of short strings. Prefer repository-relative paths or clear component names.

agent.prompt_template:
Runtime task:
{{task}}

Inspect target: {{item}}
Report integration risks, missing tests, and concrete findings. Be concise.

nodes.prompt_template:
Runtime task:
{{task}}

Plan:
{{outputs.plan}}

Inspections:
{{outputs.inspect}}

Synthesize a clear recommendation. Return structured JSON with ok (boolean), verdict (string), and findings (array of strings).
